00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:44,960
you're tailing someone?

299
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:45,879
Who?

300
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:46,919
Don't ask what you shouldn't.

301
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,360
You're supposed to be undercover,

302
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,840
yet here you are actually going on a real date?

303
00:10:50,639 --> 00:10:51,159
No, wait,

304
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,039
would you believe me if I said this was an accident?

305
00:10:53,279 --> 00:10:54,000
I just happened to be at this table

306
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:54,840
when he came over.

307
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,279
Are you kidding me?

308
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:56,759
Come on,

309
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,559
are you making a fool of me?

310
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,679
Just go through the motions.

311
00:11:01,879 --> 00:11:02,960
Don't cause trouble for them.

312
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:05,320
I...

313
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:06,960
Fine, for your sake,

314
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,840
I won't hold it against them.

315
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,039
Mister

316
00:11:16,279 --> 00:11:16,919
Tell me

317
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:18,679
Do I look like the woman you once loved?

318
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,080
Call me big brother

319
00:11:21,879 --> 00:11:22,480
Big brother

320
00:11:23,639 --> 00:11:24,720
Can you tell me

321
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,120
the story between you two?

322
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:28,279
When she was young

323
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,039
she was just like you

324
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,039
Beautiful, gentle

325
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,080
and all alone in the world

326
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,279
Back then

327
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,679
I was just a small-time boss

328
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,519
I helped her out in life

329
00:11:37,519 --> 00:11:39,720
and later we ended up together

330
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:40,639
And after that

331
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:42,600
my business kept getting bigger

332
00:11:42,879 --> 00:11:45,519
With more money, my horizons broadened

333
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:47,200
And when I looked back

334
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,720
I had already lost her

335
00:11:48,919 --> 00:11:50,480
What a tragically beautiful story

336
00:11:56,559 --> 00:11:57,840
You know, in this life

337
00:11:58,159 --> 00:12:01,240
we always think the next restaurant tastes better

338
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:03,399
But after you've tried every delicacy

339
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:05,480
you realize the best food

340
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:07,519
is still simple home cooking

341
00:12:07,519 --> 00:12:09,519
That's exactly how I feel now

342
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,440
The woman who suits me best

343
00:12:11,759 --> 00:12:12,480
is still her

344
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,360
Then it seems

345
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:16,720
your relationship with your current wife

346
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,559
has serious problems

347
00:12:17,559 --> 00:12:18,759
No, no, no

348
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:21,159
My current wife is wonderful

349
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:25,279
But something just seems to be missing

350
00:12:25,279 --> 00:12:26,240
Maybe it's because

351
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:28,320
she's too obedient, too indulgent with me

352
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,960
Right now we're out drinking

353
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:31,759
and she doesn't even care

354
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,159
Then do you think

355
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:35,639
the kind of woman who nags you every day

356
00:12:35,639 --> 00:12:36,440
who makes a fuss with you

357
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,559
is the one who truly loves you?

358
00:12:37,759 --> 00:12:39,120
When I was young

359
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:41,720
I hated being controlled by anyone

360
00:12:42,399 --> 00:12:44,039
That's why I broke up with her

361
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,960
But later I realized

362
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,399
only when she cares

363
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:49,399
will she nag you

364
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,159
If she doesn't

365
00:12:50,279 --> 00:12:51,200
then she only

366
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,559
cares about your money

367
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,440
and not necessarily you yourself

368
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,039
Your wife is here

369
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:02,519
Why is she ignoring you?

370
00:13:02,879 --> 00:13:03,480
See

371
00:13:03,639 --> 00:13:04,879
She doesn't care about me, does she?

372
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,919
But there's another possibility

373
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:08,519
She cares about me a lot

374
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:11,360
and wants to get my attention

375
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,720
How about this

376
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:14,399
Mister

377
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:16,399
Let's

378
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,840
make your wife jealous

379
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,879
make her get

380
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:23,120
super jealous over you, how about it?

381
00:13:23,639 --> 00:13:25,720
Let's see if she really doesn't care

382
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:26,440
or whether

383
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:27,799
she actually does care about you

384
00:13:27,799 --> 00:13:28,919
You're so naughty

385
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:30,960
Come, let's drink

386
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:39,240
You two are really using me as a pawn

387
00:13:39,799 --> 00:13:41,320
Hey, hey, why isn't the bill being settled?

388
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:41,840
Tianfang

389
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:42,559
We've got a mission

390
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:46,960
Handsome

391
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:48,320
Come here

392
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,399
Ms. Xu

393
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:51,600
Yes, go ahead

394
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,000
You're the manager, right?

395
00:13:55,399 --> 00:13:57,120
So satisfying the customer's requests

396
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,159
is part of your job, isn't it?

397
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:58,919
Of course

398
00:13:59,080 --> 00:13:59,879
What do you need?

399
00:14:02,039 --> 00:14:02,559
Well

400
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,279
Have a drink with me

401
00:14:04,559 --> 00:14:04,960
Wait

402
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:05,720
Here's a tip

403
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:06,279
Take it

404
00:14:13,559 --> 00:14:14,879
Ms. Xu, be careful

405
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:16,519
Why am I feeling a bit dizzy?

